text: Theresa Senff (born 2 February 1982) is a road cyclist from Germany. She represented her nation at the 2003, 2004, 2005 and 2006 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:People from Arnstadt Category:People from Bezirk Erfurt Category:German female cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Thuringia
